title: EYL #205 LaRussell on Offer Based Business, Giving Fans Streaming Revenue, & Independence
itunes:title: EYL #205 LaRussell on Offer Based Business, Giving Fans Streaming Revenue, & Independence
description:
In this episode we spoke with the young legend LaRussell. He talked about his offer based business model, and how he's changing the landscape of the music industry. We also talked about him giving fans ownership in his music, marketing, social media, therapy and more. #larussell #music #independentartist
